275
00:17:18,280 --> 00:17:21,920
they would not be able to get any idea of that house at all

276
00:17:21,990 --> 00:17:23,780
You would have to say to them

277
00:17:24,270 --> 00:17:27,270
I saw a house that cost $20000

278
00:17:27,630 --> 00:17:29,170
Then they would exclaim

279
00:17:29,600 --> 00:17:32,620
ohwhat a pretty house that is

280
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:36,240
Just so you might say to them

281
00:17:36,890 --> 00:17:40,780
the proof that the little prince existed is that he was charming

282
00:17:40,800 --> 00:17:41,880
that he left

283
00:17:41,900 --> 00:17:43,800
and that he was looking for a sheep

284
00:17:44,120 --> 00:17:45,960
If anybody wants a sheep

285
00:17:45,980 --> 00:17:48,210
that is a proof that he exists

286
00:17:48,990 --> 00:17:55,230
And what good would it do to tell them that they would shrug their shoulders and treat you like a child

287
00:17:55,780 --> 00:18:01,690
But if you said to them the planet he came from is asteroid B 602

288
00:18:02,130 --> 00:18:06,190
then they would be convinced and leave you in peace from their questions

289
00:18:07,250 --> 00:18:08,640
They are like that

290
00:18:08,870 --> 00:18:11,310
