294
00:18:27,850 --> 00:18:38,130
I should have liked to say once upon a time there was a little prince who lived on a planet that was scarcely any bigger than himself

295
00:18:38,290 --> 00:18:47,840
and who had need of a sheep to those who understand life that would have given a much greater air of truth to my story

296
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:52,400
for I do not want anyone to read my book carelessly

297
00:18:52,940 --> 00:18:57,480
