298
00:18:58,330 --> 00:19:03,980
Six years have already passed since my friend went away from me with his sheep

299
00:19:04,620 --> 00:19:13,260
If I try to describe him here it is to make sure that I shall not forget him to forget a friend is sad

300
00:19:13,450 --> 00:19:15,760
not everyone has had a friend

301
00:19:16,250 --> 00:19:18,080
and if I forget him

302
00:19:18,340 --> 00:19:24,620
