00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:58,230
as I learned

364
00:22:58,280 --> 00:23:01,610
there were on the planet where the little prince lived

365
00:23:01,760 --> 00:23:03,240
as on all planets

366
00:23:03,520 --> 00:23:06,090
good plants and bad plants

367
00:23:06,740 --> 00:23:07,900
In consequence

