371
00:23:24,910 --> 00:23:27,980
Then this little seed will stretch itself and begin

372
00:23:28,490 --> 00:23:29,970
timidly at first

373
00:23:30,030 --> 00:23:34,870
to push a charming little sprig inoffensively upward toward the sun

