00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:40,330
if it is only a sprout of radish or the sprig of a rose bush

375
00:23:40,500 --> 00:23:43,050
1 would let it grow wherever it might wish

376
00:23:43,650 --> 00:23:45,590
But when it is a bad plant

377
00:23:45,600 --> 00:23:48,810
one must destroy it as soon as possible

378
00:23:49,050 --> 00:23:52,240
the very first instant that one recognizes it

379
00:23:53,360 --> 00:23:58,840
Now there were some terrible seeds on the planet that was the home of the little prince

