00:25:02,460 --> 00:25:10,610
but very easy and one day he said to me you ought to make a beautiful drawing

396
00:25:10,710 --> 00:25:19,440
so that the children where you live can see exactly how all this is that would be very useful to them if they were to travel someday

397
00:25:19,840 --> 00:25:26,330
sometimes he added there is no harm in putting off a piece of work until another day

398
00:25:26,780 --> 00:25:29,030
but when it is a matter of baobabs

