404
00:26:18,750 --> 00:26:29,600
and so it is for them that I have worked so hard over this drawing the lesson which I pass on by this means is worth all the trouble it has cost me

405
00:26:30,520 --> 00:26:38,990
perhaps you will ask me why are there no other drawings in this book as magnificent and impressive as this drawing of the baobabs

406
00:26:39,670 --> 00:26:43,800
the reply is simple I have tried

407
00:26:44,280 --> 00:26:56,450
