00:27:39,760 --> 00:27:43,420
At first you seemed to be very much surprised

423
00:27:43,510 --> 00:27:45,810
and then you laughed to yourself

424
00:27:45,850 --> 00:27:50,040
you said to me I am always thinking that I am at home

425
00:27:50,620 --> 00:27:55,400
just so everybody knows that when it is noon in the United States

