429
00:28:07,060 --> 00:28:11,350
UnfortunatelyFrance is too far away for that

430
00:28:11,750 --> 00:28:13,590
but on your tiny planet

431
00:28:13,600 --> 00:28:14,670
my little prince

432
00:28:15,010 --> 00:28:18,700
all you need to do is move your chair a few steps

433
00:28:19,550 --> 00:28:24,200
you can see the day end and the twilight falling whenever you like

434
00:28:25,240 --> 00:28:27,320
One day you said to me

435
00:28:27,800 --> 00:28:33,760
I saw the sunset 44 times and a little later you added

436
00:28:34,340 --> 00:28:35,160
you know

437
00:28:35,170 --> 00:28:38,860
one loves the sunset when one is so sad

438
00:28:39,850 --> 00:28:40,940
Were you so sad

439
00:28:40,940 --> 00:28:45,380
Then I asked on the day of the 44 sunsets

440
00:28:46,230 --> 00:28:49,270
but the little prince made no reply

441
00:28:53,040 --> 00:28:56,340
Seven on the fifth day

442
00:28:56,350 --> 00:28:58,030
Againas always

443
00:28:58,710 --> 00:29:00,460
it was thanks to the sheep

444
00:29:00,480 --> 00:29:05,440
The secret of the little prince's life was revealed to me abruptly

445
00:29:05,460 --> 00:29:07,560
without anything to lead up to it

446
00:29:07,710 --> 00:29:13,130
and as if the question had been born of long and science meditation on his problem

447
00:29:13,290 --> 00:29:16,500
he demanded a sheep

448
00:29:16,770 --> 00:29:18,600
If it eats little bushes

449
00:29:18,900 --> 00:29:20,730
