01:59:36,100 --> 01:59:38,060
but he made one more effort

2223
01:59:38,920 --> 01:59:41,870
You know it will be very nice

2224
01:59:42,240 --> 01:59:44,710
I too shall look at the stars

2225
01:59:45,000 --> 01:59:48,440
All the stars will be wells with a rusty pulley

2226
01:59:48,580 --> 01:59:52,790
All the stars will pour out fresh water for me to drink

2227
01:59:53,820 --> 01:59:55,100
I said nothing

2228
01:59:56,480 --> 01:59:58,430
that will be so amusing

2229
01:59:58,480 --> 02:00:06,030
You will have 500 million little bells and I shall have 500 million springs of fresh water

2230
02:00:07,640 --> 02:00:11,670
and he too said nothing more because he was crying

2231
02:00:12,640 --> 02:00:13,820
Here it is

2232
02:00:14,020 --> 02:00:16,080
let me go on by myself

2233
02:00:17,170 --> 02:00:20,100
And he sat down because he was afraid

2234
02:00:21,000 --> 02:00:22,530
Then he said again

2235
02:00:23,160 --> 02:00:24,290
you know

2236
02:00:24,490 --> 02:00:25,600
my flower

2237
02:00:26,120 --> 02:00:30,220
I am responsible for her and she is so weak

2238
02:00:30,240 --> 02:00:32,080
she is so naive

2239
02:00:32,180 --> 02:00:38,390
She has four thorns of no use at all to protect herself against all the world

2240
02:00:39,670 --> 02:00:47,220
I too sat down because I was not able to stand up any longer there

2241
02:00:47,490 --> 02:00:49,320
Now that is all

2242
02:00:50,340 --> 02:00:52,250
He still hesitated a little

2243
02:00:52,260 --> 02:00:53,320
then he got up

2244
02:00:53,580 --> 02:00:55,070
he took one step

2245
02:00:55,370 --> 02:00:56,890
I could not move

2246
02:00:57,790 --> 02:01:01,420
there was nothing but a flash of yellow close to his ankle

2247
02:01:01,940 --> 02:01:04,220
He remained motionless for an instant

2248
02:01:04,550 --> 02:01:06,320
he did not cry out

2249
02:01:06,730 --> 02:01:09,870
he fell as gently as a tree falls

2250
02:01:10,010 --> 02:01:13,840
there was not even any sound because of the sand

2251
02:01:18,560 --> 02:01:25,040
27 and now six years have already gone by

2252
02:01:25,510 --> 02:01:28,130
I have never yet told this story

2253
02:01:28,710 --> 02:01:33,280
The companions who met me on my return were well content to see me alive

2254
02:01:33,920 --> 02:01:35,080
I was sad

2255
02:01:35,260 --> 02:01:38,350
but I told them I am tired

2256
02:01:39,220 --> 02:01:42,180
Now my sorrow is comforted a little

2257
02:01:42,540 --> 02:01:43,710
that is to say

2258
02:01:43,750 --> 02:01:45,520
not entirely

2259
02:01:46,140 --> 02:01:52,090
but I know that he did go back to his planet because I did not find his body at daybreak

2260
02:01:52,510 --> 02:01:54,620
It was not such a heavy body

2261
02:01:55,140 --> 02:01:57,940
and at night I loved to listen to the stars

2262
02:01:58,310 --> 02:02:02,820
It is like 500 million little bells

2263
02:02:04,260 --> 02:02:10,080
but there is one extraordinary thing when I drew the muzzle for the little prince

2264
02:02:10,660 --> 02:02:13,530
I forgot to add the leather strap to it

2265
02:02:13,820 --> 02:02:17,550
He will never have been able to fasten it on his sheep

2266
02:02:18,220 --> 02:02:22,600
So now I keep wondering what is happening on his planet

2267
02:02:22,900 --> 02:02:27,100
Perhaps the sheep has eaten the flower at one time

2268
02:02:27,100 --> 02:02:28,270
I say to myself

2269
02:02:28,280 --> 02:02:29,440
surely not

2270
02:02:29,450 --> 02:02:36,020
the little prince shuts his flower under her glass globe every night and he watches over his sheep very carefully

2271
02:02:36,680 --> 02:02:38,650
then I am happy

2272
02:02:39,140 --> 02:02:43,000
and there is sweetness in the laughter of all the stars

2273
02:02:43,720 --> 02:02:46,480
But at another time I say to myself

2274
02:02:46,950 --> 02:02:50,310
at some moment or other one is absent minded

2275
02:02:50,370 --> 02:02:51,850
and that is enough

2276
02:02:52,380 --> 02:02:55,300
On some one evening he forgot the glass globe

2277
02:02:55,340 --> 02:02:58,560
or the sheep got out without making any noise in the night

2278
02:02:59,650 --> 02:03:02,520
and then the little bells are changed to tears

2279
02:03:03,430 --> 02:03:03,860
Here

2280
02:03:03,860 --> 02:03:07,520
thenis a great mystery for you

2281
02:03:07,530 --> 02:03:09,590
who also love the little prince

2282
02:03:09,600 --> 02:03:10,620
and for me

2283
02:03:10,780 --> 02:03:22,780
nothing in the universe can be the same if somewhere we do not know where a sheep that we never saw has yes or no Eaton arose

2284
02:03:25,120 --> 02:03:26,720
Look up at the sky

2285
02:03:27,200 --> 02:03:28,470
Ask yourselves

2286
02:03:28,580 --> 02:03:30,800
is it yes or no

2287
02:03:31,180 --> 02:03:33,460
Has the sheep eaten the flour

2288
02:03:34,010 --> 02:03:36,930
And you will see how everything changes

2289
02:03:37,830 --> 02:03:44,040
And no grownup will ever understand that this is a matter of so much importance

2290
02:03:44,510 --> 02:03:45,880
This is to me

2291
02:03:45,990 --> 02:03:49,680
the loveliest and saddest landscape in the world

2292
02:03:50,190 --> 02:03:53,440
It is the same as that on the preceding page

2293
02:03:53,720 --> 02:03:57,190
but I have drawn it again to impress it on your memory

2294
02:03:57,670 --> 02:04:02,290
It is here that the little Prince appeared on earth and disappeared

2295
02:04:02,730 --> 02:04:10,480
Look at it carefully so that you will be sure to recognize it in case you travel someday to the African desert

2296
02:04:10,960 --> 02:04:13,620
and if you should come upon this spot

2297
02:04:14,180 --> 02:04:16,010
please do not hurry on

2298
02:04:16,390 --> 02:04:20,400
Wait for a time exactly under the star

2299
02:04:22,120 --> 02:04:25,220
Thenif a little man appears who laughs

2300
02:04:25,330 --> 02:04:26,980
who has golden hair

2301
02:04:27,010 --> 02:04:29,270
and who refuses to answer questions

2302
02:04:29,540 --> 02:04:31,400
you will know who he is

2303
02:04:31,980 --> 02:04:33,310
If this should happen

2304
02:04:33,610 --> 02:04:35,010
please comfort me

2305
02:04:35,470 --> 02:04:38,440
send me word that he has come back

